name: BrucellosisTestsForBrucellaSpeciesAntibodyQuantitative
title: Brucellosis (Tests for Brucella species Antibody [Quantitative])
purpose:
(Clinical Focus: This set of values contains codes for laboratory test names associated with detecting the presence of Brucella Total Antibody),(Data Element Scope: Laboratory tests names that were ordered or observed.),(Inclusion Criteria: component: Brucella Total Antibody;  

LOINC search: Brucella Ab Qn -milk -whey -interpretation -panel),(Exclusion Criteria: specimens: milk whey;  test type = interpretation or panels)
